  "title": "The Garden Variety Show",
  "description": "Drag story hour but with puppets! For gardeners, kids, and grownup campy kids, it’s a puppet cabaret! Starring Sorrel and Arugula (the Bitter Sisters), Buddy May Bloom (that's his name!) Invasion of the Lilies of the Valley, Todd the Lady Bug, La Composta, and the dancing Carrettes! #thegardenvarietyshow",
  "credits": "<strong>Playwright</strong>: Gabriel Quirk<br/><strong>Director</strong>: Gabriel Quirk<br/><strong>Cast</strong>: Gabriel Quirk<br/><strong>Designers</strong>: Gabriel Quirk<br/>",
  "website": "https://gabrielq.com | FB The Garden Variety Show",
